document_data.name: Gaerul's Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Gaerul's Street''' was a road found within the city of [[Suldolphor]] in far eastern [[Calimshan]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Suldolphor}}
document_data.Location: Gaerul's Street ran through southwest Suldolphor near the harbor.
document_data.Notable Locations: [[Emerald Dragon Way]] branched north from Gaerul's Street.
